class Layer {

    visible = true;
    name = undefined;
    imghash = undefined;
    image = undefined;
    rotation = 0;
    rect = {
        top: 0,
        left: 0,
        height: 0,
        width: 0
    }

    appliedEffects = []

    constructor(layername, imghash, img) {
        this.name = layername;
        this.imghash = imghash;
        this.visible = true;

        var i = new Image();
        var caller = this;
        i.onload = () => {
            caller.rect = {
                top: 0,
                left: 0,
                height: i.height,
                width: i.width
            }
        }
        i.src = img;
        this.image = i;
    }

}
